# Simple Calculator Microservice

This is a simple calculator microservice built using Node.js and Express. It provides basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division via RESTful API endpoints.

## Table of Contents
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [API Endpoints](#api-endpoints)
- [Error Handling](#error-handling)
- [Contributing](#contributing)

## Installation

### Prerequisites
Ensure that you have the following installed:
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/en/download/)
- [Git](https://git-scm.com/)
- A code editor such as [Visual Studio Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/)

### Steps to Install
1. Clone this repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/sit323-2025-prac4p.git
